  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <lg xml:id="TolC404">
        <l>niraṉiṟai cuṇṇa maṭimaṟi moḻimāṟ</l>
	<l>ṟavaināṉ keṉpa moḻipuṇa riyalpē.</l>
      </lg>
    </body>
  </text>

  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Iḷampūraṇar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Namaccivāya Mutaliyār</persName> 1931, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/216/mode/1up">216</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/216/mode/1up">216</ref>.</p>
<p>eṉpatu, niraṉiṟai, cuṇṇam, aṭimaṟi, moḻimāṟṟu eṉa nāṉku vakaiyāṉ moḻikaḷ tammuḷ puṇaruñ ceyyuḷakattu eṉpatu uṇarttiyavāṟu.</p>
<p>avaiyāmāṟu avaṟṟavaṟṟuc ciṟappuc cūttiraṅkaḷāl aṟika. 	(8)</p>
    </body>
  </text>

  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Cēṉāvaraiyar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Ci. Vai. Tāmōtarampiḷḷai</persName> 1868, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n257/mode/1up">254</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n257/mode/1up">254</ref>.</p>
  <p>iṉic ceyyuḷiṭattu vikāravakaiyāṉ moḻikaḷ tam muṭpuṇarumāṟu kūṟukiṉṟār.</p>
  <p>i-ḷ. niraṉiṟaiyum, cuṇṇamum, aṭimaṟiyum, moḻi māṟṟumeṉa nāṉkeṉṟu collupa, annāṉkucolluñ ceyyuḷiṭattut tammuṭpuṇarumuṟaimai. e-ṟu.</p>
  <p>nāṉkucollumeṉpatūuñ ceyyuḷiṭatteṉpatūum atikārattāṟpeṟṟām.</p>
  <p>niraṉiṟaiyuñ cuṇṇamum moḻimāṟṟātalokkumāyiṉum, niraṉiṟṟalum aḷavaṭiyeṇcīraic cuṇṇamākat tuṇittalumākiya vēṟupāṭuṭaimaiyāṉ, avaṟṟaip pirittu avvēṟupāṭṭāṟ peyar koṭuttu, vēṟilakkaṇamillāta moḻimāṟṟai moḻimāṟṟeṉṟār.</p>
  <p>iccūttirattāṉ moḻipuṇariyal nāṉkeṉa varaiyaṟuttavāṟu.	(8)</p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Nacciṉārkkiṉiyar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Irāma. Kōvintacāmipiḷḷai</persName> 1997, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZM3kZpy.TVA_BOK_0008472/page/382/mode/1up">382</ref>―<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZM3kZpy.TVA_BOK_0008472/page/382/mode/1up">382</ref>.</p>
<p>itu, ceyyuḷ ceyvaḻi yataṉporuṭkiṭai kūṟukiṉṟatu.</p>
<p>(i-ḷ) iyalpupuṇarmoḻi - iyaṟkaiyākat tammuṭ kūṭip poruḷuṇarttuñ coṟka ḷaṅṅaṉa miyaṟkaiyākak kūṭip poruḷuṇarttātu vikārappaṭṭup poruḷuṇarttuṅkāl, avai-avvikāra vakai, niraṉiṟai cuṇṇa maṭi maṟi moḻimāṟṟu nāṉkeṉpa - niraṉiṟaiyuñ cuṇṇamu maṭimaṟiyu moḻi māṟṟu meṉa nāṉkeṉṟu kūṟuvarāciriya reṉṟavāṟu.</p>
<p>niraṉiṟaiyuñ cuṇṇamum, niralē niṟuttalun tuṇittuk kūṭṭutalumākiya vēṟupāṭuṭaimaiyiṉ, moḻimāṟṟiṉ vēṟāyiṟṟu. (8)</p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Teyvaccilaiyār</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">1929, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZU1k0My.TVA_BOK_0007188/page/n229/mode/1up">222</ref>―<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZU1k0My.TVA_BOK_0007188/page/n230/mode/1up">223</ref>.</p>
<p>ceyyuḷakattup poruḷuṇarac coṟṟoṭukkumāṟu uṇarttutal nutaliṟṟu.</p>
<p>i-ḷ :- niraṉiṟaiyum, cuṇṇamum, aṭimaṟiyum, moḻi māṟṟum eṉa nāṉkeṉṟu collupa poruḷ puṇarumeṉa moḻipuṇarkkum iyal. e-ṟu.</p>
<p>ceyyuḷakattut tirintu poruḷpaṭuñcol eṭuttōtiṉār: vaḻakkiṉkaṇ iyalpākic, ceyyuṭkaṇṇum iyalpāki naṭakkum poruḷkaḷ ōtavēṇṭāmaiyiṉ. avaiyāmāṟu tattam ciṟappuc cūttirattuṭ kāṭṭutum.	(8)</p>
    </body>
  </text>
  
